# games_bundled/: ships only OUR OWN data (game specs, terrain derivation,
# scenarios, engine-generated setup saves). Third-party module art — maps,
# counters, module-provided saves — is NEVER committed (Bruce 2026-07-12,
# Decision Games copyright compliance; art purged from history same day).
# Stage art locally from your own module copy via build_stage.py.
dist/*
*.exe
!games_bundled/**/*.json
!games_bundled/blue-and-gray-chickamauga/setup.vsav
!games_bundled/westwall-arnhem/setup.vsav
